videos.description: Derrius Guice run for 1 yd for a TD
videos.headline: LSU strikes first with strong goal line TD

videos.description: Austin Appleby pass complete to Tyrie Cleveland for 13 yds to the LSU 45 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: Appleby escapes pressure to convert 1st down

videos.description: LSU's leading tackler Kendell Beckwith leaves game with injury
videos.headline: LSU's leading tackler Kendell Beckwith leaves game with injury

videos.description: After initial speculation that he would not play due to injury, Leonard Fournette enters the game and runs 9 yards on his first touch of the game.
videos.headline: Fournette runs 9 yards on first touch of game

videos.description: D.J. Chark run for 29 yds to the Fla 18 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: LSU runs end around for 29 yards

videos.description: Derrius Guice run for a loss of 4 yards to the Fla 11 Derrius Guice fumbled, forced by Caleb Brantley, recovered by Fla Kylan Johnson
videos.headline: Florida recovers fumbles in the Red Zone

videos.description: Leonard Fournette run for 1 yd to the LSU 49
videos.headline: Florida defender jumps into pile like jumping into pile of leaves

videos.description: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron discusses Leonard Fournette's toughness
videos.headline: LSU head coach Ed Orgeron discusses Leonard Fournette's toughness

videos.description: Danny Etling pass complete to Malachi Dupre for 33 yds to the Fla 24 for a 1ST down
videos.headline: LSU Receiver makes makes leaping reception and stays in bounds

videos.description: LSU's Danny Etling is shoved out of bounds at the 1-yard line by a Florida defender, preventing a third-quarter touchdown.
videos.headline: Florida defender lands big TD-saving hit

videos.description: Florida's Tyrie Cleveland grabs QB Austin Appleby's first-down throw and takes it to the house for a 98-yard touchdown against LSU.
videos.headline: Gators receiver sheds tackler on 98-yard TD run

videos.description: LSU punter Josh Growden sends the ball 43 yards and after hitting the pylon, it bounces out of bounds, leaving Florida at the 1-yard line.
videos.headline: LSU's punt hits pylon, pins Florida at the 1-yard line

videos.headline: LSU's Guice cuts his way through the Florida defense
